---
import { savingsRows } from "@/config/tax-advisory-presentation";
---

<section class="bg-white py-16 sm:py-20">
  <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-7xl gap-10 px-5 sm:px-6 lg:grid-cols-[0.9fr_1.1fr] lg:items-center">
    <div data-animate="fade-up">
      <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-primary-800 sm:text-sm">
        Estimated tax calculator
      </p>
      <h2 class="mt-4 font-heading text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-950 sm:text-4xl">
        Make the overpayment conversation concrete before filing.
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-5 text-base leading-7 text-gray-600">
        The presentation points out that many clients overpay because strategy,
        bookkeeping, implementation, and documentation are not connected early
        enough. The estimate gives the client a planning target, not a guarantee.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="rounded-lg border border-gray-200 bg-gray-50 p-4 shadow-sm sm:p-5" data-animate="scale-in">
      <div class="rounded-lg bg-white p-5">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-4 border-b border-gray-100 pb-4">
          <div>
            <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-primary-700">
              Example analysis
            </p>
            <h3 class="mt-1 font-heading text-xl font-bold text-gray-950">
              Tax burden comparison
            </h3>
          </div>
          <span class="rounded-full bg-accent-100 px-3 py-1 text-sm font-semibold text-accent-700">
            Draft
          </span>
        </div>
        <dl class="mt-5 grid gap-4">
          {savingsRows.map((number) => (
            <div
              class:list={[
                "rounded-lg border p-4",
                number.highlight
                  ? "border-primary-200 bg-primary-50"
                  : "border-gray-100 bg-white",
              ]}
            >
              <div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-4">
                <dt class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-600">{number.label}</dt>
                <dd
                  class:list={[
                    "font-heading text-xl font-bold sm:text-2xl",
                    number.highlight ? "text-primary-800" : "text-gray-950",
                  ]}
                >
                  {number.amount}
                </dd>
              </div>
              <div class="mt-3 h-2.5 overflow-hidden rounded-full bg-gray-100" aria-hidden="true">
                <div
                  class:list={[
                    "h-full rounded-full",
                    number.highlight ? "bg-accent-500" : "bg-primary-500",
                  ]}
                  style={`width: ${number.width}`}
                >
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          ))}
        </dl>
        <p class="mt-4 text-sm leading-6 text-gray-600">
          Example only. Actual savings depend on facts, timing, entity structure,
          income, records, and whether the strategy is implemented correctly.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
